rect.id: We will ask you all the necessary questions allowing us to turn your requests into specific tasks. When all the tasks are outlined, we will proceed with the correct solution installation. Then we need to create CRM users and set up work with mail and file storage.

From the basic settings, we will move on to creating CRM functionality to unite and streamline the main business processes of your client care department and display this functionality in an easy-to-read and suitable way. Also, we need to provide employees with different levels of access to the system according to their responsibilities. After that, your team can start using your CRM for improved customer service.

We are going to train your staff to be productive at work with the system. Plus, during the agreed time after the successful CRM implementation, the UDS team will be in touch with you to handle any CRM issues.

For those whose needs go beyond the UDS Quick Start Customer Service, we provide a range of additional services. You can book some of them right away, for example, data migration from your `old` system. Or you are welcome to discuss the extended services after all the stages of the Quick Start are successfully performed. If one day you decide to grow the capabilities of your Dynamics 365 Customer Systems, we will surely consult you on worthwhile actions for your particular case. It may be the creation of a user-friendly portal for your customers or the integration of your CRM with some third-party tools popular within your company.
